Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.99,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,雖然沒有明顯外傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:24.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是父親的頭部受到撞擊  失去意識
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:28.88,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,賢治從昏迷中醒來後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.52,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,他變得跟過去判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.39,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,他的主體性和定向力大幅降低
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.52,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,推測頭部因強烈的衝擊而產生了障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:45.17,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,因此  我告訴家屬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.15,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,讓超級 AI MICHI 進行治療才是最有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:55.20,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是… 把人力所不能及的問題交給超級 AI 處理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.13,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,這是我父親最討厭的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:07.29,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,而後藤的家屬們找到的希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:13.64,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,那就是賢治的孫女  莉音的「歌聲」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:20.11,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,爺爺  你聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.06,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.82,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,繼續努力  繼續努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:30.33,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,在接觸到音樂和電影時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:36.03,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,賢治受損的迴路中  恢復了人性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:40.16,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,這是人類之手所創造的  藝術的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.62,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,後藤一家的努力才剛剛開始
Comment: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.58,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們(日本仿生人權利組織,Humanoid Rights Japan)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.58,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們日本仿生人權利組織
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.17,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不認為這是什麼值得宣傳的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.93,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,明明有治好他電子腦的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:58.18,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但家屬卻拒絕治療
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.35,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,這是對老人的忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.62,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,意識是非常敏感的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.44,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不接受超級 AI 精神治療的例子也不罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.69,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,那用人類的力量治療就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.67,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,可以嗎  須堂醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.95,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,先讓他來一趟診所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.11,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,十分感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.00,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,這種治療責任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.51,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,所以普通的醫生都是交給超級 AI 來做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.03,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是須堂醫生的醫術是值得信賴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.14,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,看起來硬體損傷並沒有很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,負責個性基礎的部位應該都沒有受損
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如果能安裝一些系統來彌補損失的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.45,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,令尊的病症應該能被治好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.66,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.13,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,現有的媒體都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.44,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們必須要成為第一手信源才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.52,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我之後再打給你  先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.29,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,醫生說能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.39,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,那麼  手術安排到哪一天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:52.10,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,不… 我們還沒決定要進行手術…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.32,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.67,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,是要安裝和以前不同的程序吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,人裝上義肢之後  不也還是同一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.06,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是義肢和電子腦不是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.18,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.74,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是在腦袋裡  也有部位是能被替換的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.04,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,所以應該也沒什麼區別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你到底在猶豫什麼  真讓人搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.78,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,明明眼前就有切實可行的治療方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.00,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我無法保證一定能恢復如初哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:30.29,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,畢竟的確有數據因物理損傷無法找回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.31,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.73,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.85,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,讓我再考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:58.24,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,夕陽中的紅蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:07.17,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,上次看到你停在人背上已是何時？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.99,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,山中田地裡的…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.19,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.56,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,須堂醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:21.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我感覺他們家不願意治好賢治  是有苦衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,苦衷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,他女兒好像想成為歌手或者藝人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以  你覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:33.53,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你是說  他們家是利用現況來換取關注？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.46,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不管有什麼苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.92,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,拒絕接受有效的治療是侵犯人權
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.43,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,他們會接受手術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.84,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.91,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,這不是我能決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.64,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,這麼晚了  是誰打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.41,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  這麼晚打來電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.66,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是我想今天內和您談談
Comment: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.02,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們(日本仿生人權利組織,Humanoid Rights Japan)認為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.02,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們日本仿生人權利組織認為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.43,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,拒絕治療後藤賢治是很嚴重的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:31.85,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,「所有人類生而自由  在尊嚴和權利上一律平等」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:38.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,1948 年簽署的 世界人權宣言的第一條如是記載
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:42.79,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,這裡的「人類」不包含仿生人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.56,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,仿生人在歷史的舞台上登場
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,與人類共同生存
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,到取得現有的人權
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.72,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,他們歷經了艱難曲折
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.47,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,最終  隨著超級 AI 的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}時代發生了巨大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.38,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,傑  追加模組的安裝已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.39,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,以我來看也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,現在進行生物軀體縫合術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.39,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你感覺還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.86,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好  那就把一切給恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.46,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,生命徵象全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.46,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,爺爺沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.97,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.81,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我們全家人一起迎接他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.68,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你也真夠纏人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.31,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.73,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:11.39,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,記錄後藤的恢復過程也是我們的活動內容嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.86,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,要把照明器材搬到二樓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.82,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,嗯  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.17,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.10,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.27,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,喂喂  這裡可是醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.89,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我可是有取得病人家屬的許可才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他們不是挺好的一家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,才不像是你所說的那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.38,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,醫生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.13,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,病人發狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:35.75,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你這個忘恩負義的蠢兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我可是全都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.89,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,賢  賢治？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:48.00,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,給我拍影片讓我出醜  你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.67,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,後藤先生 請息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.40,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.07,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,你誤會了  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.53,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,我只是想遵守你的教導
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.43,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,覺得這能成為其他患者的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.16,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你搞什麼名堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.35,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父親  請息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,麗莎  鎮定劑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.62,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.06,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,按住那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.93,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.55,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.34,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.89,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,用了接觸型麻醉劑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:21.75,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,該不會是治療出錯了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.77,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,喂！ 說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.52,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,沒有出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.73,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,醫生的醫術十分高超
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:40.53,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,沒有出錯？ 為什麼你這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.78,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,熱衷於教育的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,願意傾聽我女兒歌聲的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.30,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,還是對我大打出手的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.68,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,都是我們所熟知的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:11:00.34,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父親完全恢復如初了  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.29,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,請問  拍攝要怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:28.49,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是… 我沒做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.62,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.03,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的價值觀和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:40.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,一旦接到委託  我就會為了患者的利益全力治療
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.51,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我能做的  僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,非常抱歉我們的商品給您帶來了不便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:01.03,Default,D,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  但本公司不能為其負責
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.78,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.24,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,就算是讓程序來向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.66,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,也一點誠意都感受不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.87,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,派人類來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.41,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,最近這種越來越多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.39,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,讓我來給他們道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.21,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.37,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我來處理  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.72,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,因為精神壓力  搞得我胃疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.81,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,這種關聯可以切斷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.81,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我能做出調整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.48,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但要是把這些身體的信號全部屏蔽掉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.32,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,哦  我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.95,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,這樣就會注意不到自己的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:48.84,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,在某一天到了極限突然崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.77,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,這工作真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.88,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,啊  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,歸根結底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:58.09,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,為什麼不能用客服 AI 來解決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.38,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那種業務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.52,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,AI 的應對當然是無可企及的優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.03,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,但是  想要賠禮道歉的人裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.68,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,也有很在意對方是不是「真人」的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:15.19,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,其中有些人要是知道我是仿生人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.48,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,「你的賠禮道歉與程序向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.35,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,有什麼區別嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.57,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,這種時候應該讓人類來道歉才對吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.62,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,就會大言不慚地說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.47,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,雖說我覺得自己也不適合這份工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我換了種咖啡豆  要喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.17,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.12,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.65,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,剛才那位… 不會有問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我希望他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.88,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,以他的情況  光是對症治療是沒法治本的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.82,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.12,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,所以才說你是廢物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.34,Default,Drunk B,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.31,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.38,Default,Drunk C,0,0,0,,喂  打起精神來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.43,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.12,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.05,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.57,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,我馬上去您那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.57,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,好的  好的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:11.26,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,能勝任這項工作的  就只有無心的機器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.15,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,辭職吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.91,Default,President,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.82,Default,President,0,0,0,,公司也意識到了你壓力的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.26,Default,President,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.73,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我很高興您能這麼說  但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.70,Default,President,0,0,0,,先聽我說完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:43.79,Default,President,0,0,0,,我們把客服的「人類」外包給了專業人士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.65,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,在這個時代  自己建房子住的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.13,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,都是非常有講究的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:57.28,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我自認為我應對顧客時  也是保持了專業素養的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.93,Default,President,0,0,0,,不不  我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.56,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,不要逼我再說一遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:08.69,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,你們公司虛擬實境的還原度就是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.95,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,我還以為你們能造得一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:21.19,Default,President,0,0,0,,今後  你和你的部下都不用再應對這些惡意顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.85,Default,President,0,0,0,,可以再考慮下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.01,Default,Comaplainer B,0,0,0,,都說了  我還要說幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:34.32,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,叫人類過來確認啊  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:53.00,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,在應對受冒犯的顧客這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.53,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,我們有進行特別的針對性訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:00.96,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,所以說  你真的沒必要和他們一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:05.04,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,姑且  這還是第一次轉給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:09.14,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,為了防止意外情況  我在外面等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.05,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.54,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,這次給您造成了困擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.49,Default,Both,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.37,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,真是的  你讓我等多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:33.69,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,我們可以通過工作人員的植入物查看現場的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:38.25,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,他們的應對方式都是按手冊行事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:47.12,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,這東西  怎麼看都不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.66,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.50,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,這個顏色數值是在誤差範圍內啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.47,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,這樣啊  照明的色溫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.68,Default,Comapliner B,0,0,0,,你看  完全不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.03,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,這個數值也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.11,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,那再確認一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.77,Default,Comapliner B,0,0,0,,無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.68,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,我也確認一下克耳文值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.70,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:19.20,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  請再稍候片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.88,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:22.91,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.96,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,真是的  怎麼看這都跟我要的壁紙不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:33.52,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,喂  你們難道認為我是不講理的魔鬼顧客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.09,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.45,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.26,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,所以  你們要怎麼賠禮道歉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.52,Default,Apologier A,0,0,0,,就結論而言  我們無法道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.77,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,喂  你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.79,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,這種壁紙給人的觀感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.28,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,會隨著照明的色溫改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.28,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,你小子怎麼還回嘴啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:05.42,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,喂喂喂  這不是讓顧客更激動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.68,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,這也是他們的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.41,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,雖然像是在回嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:15.67,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,但我這不是找藉口  而是在解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.05,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,誰要你解釋了  給我賠禮道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.09,Default,Apologizer,0,0,0,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.14,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,好吧  那我不要賠禮道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.20,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,賠禮道歉已經沒辦法收場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.86,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,都說了  照明的色溫
Comment: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.74,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,分為(燈泡色,3000K)  (溫白色,3500K)  (白色,4000K)  (晝白色,5000K)  (晝光色,6000K)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.74,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,分為燈泡色  溫白色  白色  晝白色  晝光色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.40,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,各自用克耳文作為單位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.46,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,不要跟我扯這些歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.82,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:45.20,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,你小子是怎麼對待顧客的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.96,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,這位顧客…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.99,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,您所說的一點都沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:10.23,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,實在是萬分抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:19.13,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,讓上司用暴力阻止想要講道理的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.35,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,把他作為代罪羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.52,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,這手法對這次這種投訴者是很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.62,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,你怎麼說得若無其事一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:31.37,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,就算是演技… 這也是滅絕人性的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.93,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯
